<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.10">
<l>aṉṉamuṅ kēḻa lummī ṉumāya vātiyai nākai yaḻaki yārai</l>
<l>kaṉṉinaṉ māma tiḷmaṅ kaivēntaṉ kāmaru cīrkka likaṉṟi kuṉṟā</l>
<l>viṉṉicai yālcoṉ ṉaceñcol mālai yēḻumi raṇṭumo roṉṟum vallār</l>
<l>maṉṉava rāyu lakāṇṭu mīṇṭum vāṉava rāyma kiḻvey tuvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the seven-and-two-and-one [verses]</l>
<l rend="indent">in a garland of fine words,</l>
<l>Which Kalikaṉṟi of desired esteem, king of Maṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with impenetrable good great walls, composed with flawless sweet music,</l>
<l>About the handsome one of Nākai, the primal [lord]</l>
<l rend="indent">who became a swan, boar, and fish,</l>
<l>Having ruled the earth as kings, they will then attain bliss as celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
